{"tid":1667931,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"國難條傻鳩開始走火入魔","createTime":"2019-10-21T17:04:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-01T16:45:46.000Z","uid":325757,"like":14,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"2c127bf48ef76ed0062ae8cfc3b4525c6dab5f79","tid":1667931,"uid":325757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T17:04:34.000Z","msg":"話說10月20號晚上發生左件事⋯⋯<br />\n我個手足嬲到喊￼￼～以下係佢send俾我嘅～￼<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n我屌撚死你地班左膠FA!!<br />\n救藍絲都唔緊要，人道主義我理解！<br />\n但洗唔撚洗10個人救一個死藍絲啊?<br />\n佢依家斷手定斷腳啊？洗唔洗開張手術床比你地啊？<br />\n前面啲手足嗌緊FA唔撚救，你救藍絲？<br />\n屌你個閪你同我講有好多FA手足係到？<br />\n仲屌尻我？&ldquo;FA做嘢洗唔洗你教！我地救人架！&lsquo;&rsquo;<br />\n屌你老母，你十個救一個，我一個救十個呀！<br />\n你地唔好過嚟買嘢啊！有手足唔撚救！係到企？我啲貨唔比左膠㗎！<br />\n依家企前線做FA拎光環㗎？<br />\n做唔到嘢唔好嚟買嘢！<br />\n救藍絲！一律唔賣貨啊！屌你地個閪！<br />\n<br />\n溫柔體貼可愛小公主上<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n所以亦都係因為咁，所有FA將會列入禁售行列￼￼￼￼￼，當然我認識果幾隊你哋可以繼續黎攞貨，<br />\n以上政策將會維持到直至當晚嗰幾位FA被鶳￼￼為止。<br />\n<br />\n#我係唔會比機會你地救藍絲<br />\n#見一個鶳一個<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">轉自國難fb</span>"},{"pid":"2636b6a5f731c95fa2149d30ad5236cbd19ccca2","tid":1667931,"uid":312125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T17:05:09.000Z","msg":"【文宣學堂】警完美示範「核彈都唔割」<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1667502\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1667502</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n以後見到有割席分化post，我地應即貼上巴打提議嘅金句：<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff0036e3d036ef48332b75d89074980b5aebaa56","tid":1667931,"uid":325757,"like":16,"dislike":3,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T17:07:01.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">以上政策將會維持到直至當晚嗰幾位FA被鶳￼￼為止。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n乜撚嘢意思 下面仲成堆人撐<br />\nFA救人都要被鶳？無錯 佢咁樣係做得唔夠好 但係有無嚴重到需要俾人打？你係咪痴撚線 咁都要鶳FA？"},{"pid":"6c74c5f1fcd742c987b93ad1a156786007a145ca","tid":1667931,"uid":204356,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T17:07:16.000Z","msg":"小學G？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47903c62abc7c14063da8cf14a80c447276f4e64","tid":1667931,"uid":321123,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T17:07:25.000Z","msg":"拉"},{"pid":"24412e362e9df605ee7548f1413c28c782c44569","tid":1667931,"uid":325757,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6c74c5f1fcd742c987b93ad1a156786007a145ca","tid":1667931,"uid":204356,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T17:07:16.000Z","msg":"小學G？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T17:09:40.000Z","msg":"預咗呢個post大把負皮"},{"pid":"2a08a9e67b6f8a46ce491e83e0f0684ebcc6b10a","tid":1667931,"uid":261478,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T17:12:49.000Z","msg":"阻膠FA係黑人憎嘅<br />\n人鍊保護被踢波藍絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n前線手足比狗圍住打<br />\n又唔見佢人鍊保護手足<br />\n有時好懷疑FA係唔係25仔專保護藍絲"},{"pid":"b0d8ca5839898566b33adde6757a6922badd627e","tid":1667931,"uid":4322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T17:13:51.000Z","msg":"[和理作盾] 橫掂次次都反對 咁不如次次都係早一晚先講去邊示威 配合埋其他地方大力裝修<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1667907\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1667907</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"cc76b767409d7a44fd31ec3fc2b00eb5c93baf4b","tid":1667931,"uid":325757,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2a08a9e67b6f8a46ce491e83e0f0684ebcc6b10a","tid":1667931,"uid":261478,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T17:12:49.000Z","msg":"阻膠FA係黑人憎嘅<br />\n人鍊保護被踢波藍絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno